  <sect1 id="gok-getting-started"> 
    <title>Getting Started</title> 

    <sect2 id="gok-start">
    <title>To Start &app;</title>
    <para>You can start <application>&app;</application> in the following ways:
    </para> 
    <variablelist>
    	<varlistentry>
    		<term><guimenu>Applications</guimenu> menu</term>
    		<listitem>
    		<para>Choose 
    		<menuchoice>
    		<guisubmenu>Accessibility</guisubmenu>
    		<guimenuitem>On-Screen Keyboard</guimenuitem>
    		</menuchoice>. </para>
    		</listitem>
    	</varlistentry>
    	<varlistentry>
    		<term>Command line</term>
    		<listitem>
    		<para>To start <application>&app;</application> from a command line, type the following command, 
    		then press <keycap>Return</keycap>:</para>
    		<para> 
			<command>gok</command> 
    		</para> 
    		</listitem>
    	</varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
    </sect2>
     <sect2 id="gok-when-start">
    <title>When You Start &app;</title>
    <para>When you start <application>&app;</application>, the main keyboard is displayed.</para>

